#include <iostream>
#include <string>
using namespace std;

bool find(string S1, string S2) {
	for(int i = 0; i < S2.size(); i++) {
		if (S1[i] != S2[i])
			return false;
	}
	return true;
}

int main() {
	int N, Q;
	long long int priority[1000];
	string name[1000], query;
	cin >> N;
	for(int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
		cin >> name[i] >> priority[i];
	}
	cin >> Q;
	for(int i = 0; i < Q; i++) {
		long long int max = -1000000001;
		int pos = -1;
		cin >> query;
		for(int j = 0; j < N; j++) {
			if(find(name[j], query)) {
				if(priority[j] > max) {
					max = priority[j];
					pos = j;
				}
			}
		}
		if(pos != -1)
			cout << name[pos] << endl;
		else
			cout << "NO" << endl;
	}
	return 0;
}
